    riskFactors: ["Advanced age or extremes of age","Family history of peds heent or related conditions","Chronic comorbidities (hypertension, diabetes, obesity)","Sedentary lifestyle and poor nutritional status","Tobacco, alcohol, or substance use","Immunocompromised state or prolonged medication use"],
